title: Vixen - Tori Black, Adriana Chechik (After Dark Part 2) NEW 26 S
description: Tori believes you can narrow down every decision you make to two options - and you simply take the decision that takes you the furthest - and she takes her decisions further than the rest. When Tori plays the game she likes to win. This time is no different - those who approach a decision without information are gamblers - the rest are just playing the game, and Tori is no gambler. http://imgdone.com/image/zO6AL http://imgdone.com/image/zOf8C
